thread.title: JOHNSON, JOEL

author: JOHNSON, JOEL
title: JOHNSON, JOEL
text: I have been buying coffee from Whole Latte Love or many years without and problem, In addition, I have bought three espresso machines and one drip coffee maker and have been happy with them all. They consistently have the best prices and the best products. They have espresso machines you simply don't find anywhere else. Or, to paraphrase Robert Plant, I'm gonna give 'em all of my l e.
